::Prowl::

The rockets explode against Prowl but don't go through his armor. THe
feather missiles hit Prowl in the head, denting his armor there as
well. Prowl was a huge beast in this form, and it would take more than
one set of impacts to take him down.

He spreads his wings, soaring up at Halucigen and biting again.
